---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Fruits - Dev Wells">
  <div class="min-h-screen px-phi-4 py-phi-6 max-w-[65ch] mx-auto">
    <main>
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-light tracking-tight mb-phi-4">Fruits</h1>
      <div class="space-y-phi-6">
        <article
          class="border-l-4 border-sage-200 dark:border-sage-800 pl-phi-4 py-phi-3"
        >
          <h2
            class="text-xl font-light text-sage-700 dark:text-sage-400 mb-phi-2"
          >
            Coming Soon
          </h2>
          <p class="text-bark-600 dark:text-bark-400 mb-phi-2 text-sm">
            <time>Soonâ„¢</time>
          </p>
          <p class="text-ink dark:text-ink-dark leading-relaxed">
            This space will grow with thoughts, technical posts, and
            reflections. For now, it's just soil waiting for the first seeds to
            sprout.
          </p>
        </article>

        <article
          class="border-l-4 border-sage-200 dark:border-sage-800 pl-phi-4 py-phi-3 opacity-60"
        >
          <h2
            class="text-xl font-light text-sage-700 dark:text-sage-400 mb-phi-2"
          >
            On Building Digital Gardens
          </h2>
          <p class="text-bark-600 dark:text-bark-400 mb-phi-2 text-sm">
            <time>Draft</time>
          </p>
          <p class="text-ink dark:text-ink-dark leading-relaxed">
            Why the web needs more gardens and fewer factories. A meditation on
            slow growth, organic discovery, and the joy of tending to ideas over
            time...
          </p>
        </article>

        <article
          class="border-l-4 border-sage-200 dark:border-sage-800 pl-phi-4 py-phi-3 opacity-60"
        >
          <h2
            class="text-xl font-light text-sage-700 dark:text-sage-400 mb-phi-2"
          >
            Frontend Platform Engineering
          </h2>
          <p class="text-bark-600 dark:text-bark-400 mb-phi-2 text-sm">
            <time>Draft</time>
          </p>
          <p class="text-ink dark:text-ink-dark leading-relaxed">
            Lessons learned from building tools and systems that help teams ship
            better software faster. The art of developer experience...
          </p>
        </article>
      </div>

      <footer
        class="mt-phi-8 pt-phi-6 border-t border-sage-200 dark:border-sage-800"
      >
        <p class="text-sm text-bark-500 dark:text-bark-400 text-center italic">
          "The best time to plant a tree was 20 years ago. The second best time
          is now."
        </p>
      </footer>
    </main>
  </div>
</Layout>
